<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Higher Career Academy - Joining Form</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #ff8e53, #ffffff);
            color: #333;
        }
        .joining-head {
            color: #2c3e50;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container.join {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
            color: #ff8e53;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .section-title i {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .joining-text, .joining-list {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .joining-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .joining-list .joining-info{
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .download-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .download-btn {
            background: #ff8e53;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        .download-btn:hover {
            background: #aa7e66;
        }

          
  .step {
    background: #F5F5F5;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    border-left: 4px solid #ff8e53;
    opacity: 0; /* Initially hidden */
    transform: translateX(-100%); /* Initially off-screen */
    animation: slideIn 0.5s ease-in-out forwards;
  }
  
   .step:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 0s; /* First step appears immediately */
  }
  
   .step:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.5s; /* Second step after a delay */
  }
  
  .step:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 1s; /* Third step after a delay */
  }
  
  .step:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 1.5s; /* Fourth step after a delay */
  }

  .step:nth-child(5) {
    animation-delay: 2s; /* Fourth step after a delay */
  }

  @keyframes slideIn {
    to {
      transform: translateX(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container.join {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("../includes/nav")%>

    <div class="container join">
        <h1 class="joining-head"><i class="fas fa-school"></i> Nursery Joining Form</h1>

        <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Instructions</h2>
        <p class="joining-text">Fill out this form using uppercase letters only. Ensure all fields are completed and attach the required documents as outlined. Here is a sample details which maybe needed but download the real primary joining instruction below.</p>

        <div class="step">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Personal Information</h2>
            <ul class="joining-list">
                <li class="joining-info"><strong>Student Name:</strong> __________________________</li>
                <li class="joining-info"><strong>Date of Birth:</strong> __________________________</li>
                <li class="joining-info"><strong>Gender:</strong> Male / Female</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-school"></i> Previous School Information</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>School Name:</strong> __________________________</li>
                <li><strong>Year Joined:</strong> __________________________</li>
                <li><strong>Class Reached:</strong> __________________________</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> Parent/Guardian Information</h2>
            <ul> 
                <li><strong>Full Name:</strong> __________________________</li>
                <li><strong>Address:</strong> __________________________</li>
                <li><strong>Phone Number:</strong> __________________________</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i> Required Attachments</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Copy of birth certificate</li>
                <li>Two passport-sized photos</li>
                <li>Transfer letter from previous school</li>
                <li>Progress report from previous school</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i> Payment Details</h2>
        <p>Payments are to be made through PBZ Islamic Bank, account number <strong>0726551001</strong> under the name "AB Higher Career Academic Ltd." Ensure to present the payment slip at our office for receipt issuance. No payments will be accepted at the school.</p>

        <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i> Terms and Conditions</h2>
        <p>By submitting this form, you agree to abide by the school's rules and regulations, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Timely payment of fees</li>
            <li>Ensuring the student adheres to the school's discipline and uniform policy</li>
            <li>Attending all parent meetings when called</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="download-section">
            <a href="/mnt/data/joining-Primary.doc" download class="download-btn"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download Form</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("../includes/footer")%>
</body>
</html>
